metadata.dc:description: The authors make a bibliographical study on the incidence of controlled breathing in respiratory cycles composed by short inhalations and elongated exhalations and their influence on arterial hypertension.
metadata.dc:title: Terapia respiratoria e hipertensión esencial (I).
[Respiratory therapy and essential hypertension (I)].
